Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.28,0:00:21.20,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身披天馬聖衣的你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.33,0:00:23.79,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,翱翔天際 
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.00,0:00:27.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,宛若流星
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.71,0:00:31.51,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毫無遲疑的雙眸
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.71,0:00:33.59,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泛著淚光
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.72,0:00:37.85,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不含一絲陰翳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.10,0:00:40.47,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使遍體鱗傷
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:42.98,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,縱使身死戰地
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.31,0:00:47.31,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了跨越那障壁
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.56,0:00:49.98,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們堅定不移
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.23,0:00:51.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如星辰般閃耀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.86,0:00:52.94,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星座起舞
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.15,0:00:55.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,未來的希望
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.74,0:00:56.95,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,化作指引勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:00.45,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的雙翼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.66,0:01:03.29,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓那有限的燈火
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:05.87,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,燃燒不息
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:07.46,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我們至深的羈絆
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.67,0:01:09.04,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,展現明晰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.17,0:01:11.55,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那未知的極限的前方
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.71,0:01:14.26,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是友情編織成的神話
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.42,0:01:15.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚醒奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.47,0:01:16.38,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向著未來
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.63,0:01:19.43,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,飛起
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.75,0:00:16.73,op,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光榮字幕組&galaxy
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.89,0:01:47.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的 這城堡真是大的離譜啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.85,0:01:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帕拉斯到底在哪
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.06,0:01:52.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在我們只有向前進
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.76,0:01:55.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在沙織小姐的生命燃盡之前
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.04,0:01:57.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須打倒帕拉斯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.35,0:02:07.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.10,0:02:20.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這強大的小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.74,0:02:27.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類們啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.56,0:02:35.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 你們竟然能來到這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.01,0:02:38.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你們休想通過此地
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.95,0:02:40.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個難道是
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.49,0:02:42.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聖劍？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.71,0:02:44.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擁有聖劍的刻鬥士 也就是說
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.79,0:02:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我的聖劍面前 人類會如何掙扎呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.77,0:02:57.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從劍中散溢出了小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.05,0:03:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是何等具有攻擊性的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.23,0:03:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,堅決不讓我們通過嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.85,0:03:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.48,0:03:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,見識一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.83,0:03:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我正是重爆雷斬刃的使用者 
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.20,0:03:18.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一級刻鬥士 埃該翁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.08,0:03:21.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,裝備刻衣！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.07,0:03:23.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四天王的衝擊！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.39,0:03:27.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃該翁出擊了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.86,0:03:30.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這下 聖鬥士終於可以消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:35.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是 埃該翁的目標不是聖鬥士的全滅
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.19,0:03:37.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣下去 帕拉斯大人就…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.51,0:03:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不抓緊時間的話 那位大人也就要臨近了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.22,0:03:46.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好涼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.55,0:03:47.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,冰之靈柩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.95,0:03:49.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的招數
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個非同一般的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.52,0:03:59.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昴 你究竟是什麼人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.53,0:04:00.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你問我是什麼人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.26,0:04:02.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在說什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.05,0:04:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙 認識你的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.59,0:04:07.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.86,0:04:09.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我怎麼知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.16,0:04:12.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我 我是Equuleus 
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.56,0:04:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小馬座的昴
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.57,0:04:16.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,除此之外什麼都不是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.14,0:04:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事 這小宇宙是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.42,0:04:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來和目前為止的刻鬥士不同
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.90,0:04:29.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 這彷彿重壓一般的強大小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.59,0:04:31.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,凌駕於黃金聖鬥士之上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.08,0:04:34.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙他們將要與他戰鬥嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.46,0:04:38.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連一級都出來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.49,0:04:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來走這條路似乎是猜對了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.08,0:04:43.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,猜對了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.68,0:04:46.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘛 作為對手來說 是沒什麼可抱怨的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.50,0:04:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之 既然一級都出現了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:51.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,足以見得他們也很著急
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.70,0:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著急？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.97,0:04:56.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類還真是會即刻膨脹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.67,0:04:58.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不過是想親眼目睹一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.39,0:05:06.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒了我屬下二級刻鬥士的各位的實力罷了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.60,0:05:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.75,0:05:09.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就讓你見識見識 我們的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.96,0:05:12.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且慢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.71,0:05:17.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那也讓你們見識下我埃該翁
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.85,0:05:21.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重爆雷斬刃帶來的絕望
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.19,0:05:22.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.41,0:05:28.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.59,0:05:33.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是舉起劍就…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.34,0:05:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.23,0:05:38.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.11,0:05:42.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可是賜予我等一級刻鬥士的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.04,0:05:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這把劍面前
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:46.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,連聖鬥士的最高階聖衣 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.62,0:05:49.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖衣也如同紙屑一般 
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.71,0:05:52.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,之前 你們也該見過了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:57.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,許珀裡翁的天地崩滅斬貫穿黃金聖鬥士的景象
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.01,0:06:01.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 此劍不同於彼劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我這支配重力 破壞大地的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.40,0:06:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重爆雷斬刃 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.03,0:06:09.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們根本無法碰觸 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.48,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無法接近
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.12,0:06:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在你們親身感受到此劍利刃之前
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.18,0:06:19.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的生命 就將不復存在了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.82,0:06:20.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你得逞的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.80,0:06:24.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.44,0:06:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不會允許你再傷害他們
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.62,0:06:31.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.17,0:06:33.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰座的弟弟嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.16,0:06:35.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…會提到哥哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.71,0:06:41.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰座是唯一一個傷到此劍的男人 
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.37,0:06:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我怎會忘記
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.13,0:06:47.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖然他並非憑借一己之力傷到此劍…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.41,0:06:49.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥他…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.90,0:06:52.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對人類的興趣成全了他
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.73,0:06:55.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了從鳳凰座的戰鬥能力之中
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.91,0:06:57.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看清人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.04,0:06:59.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我調整了劍的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.05,0:07:11.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到 他居然犧牲自己也要破壞劍
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,劍的傷痕是我埃凱翁的大意
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.25,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 還真是有趣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:22.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,面對明顯而壓倒性的力量差
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.94,0:07:25.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類卻仍然會抵抗 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且偶爾還會引發奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.38,0:07:29.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是非常有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.25,0:07:33.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我對人類的興趣真是無窮無盡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.16,0:07:36.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓我見識一下吧 你的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.44,0:07:40.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果可以的話 我並不想戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.15,0:07:41.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.03,0:07:43.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有人要傷害他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.26,0:07:46.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,或是阻礙他們前行
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.92,0:07:47.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會戰鬥
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.89,0:07:51.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這次不會只是讓劍受傷那麼簡單了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.57,0:07:54.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是讓人興趣盎然的發言啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.25,0:07:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.17,0:08:03.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星雲鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.59,0:08:10.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.15,0:08:16.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,旋轉防禦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.31,0:08:21.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看起來只是防禦能力比較拿手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.81,0:08:23.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不是只有防禦哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.02,0:08:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷電波濤（Thunder Wave）
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.08,0:08:32.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,彫蟲小技
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.52,0:08:35.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算對手在幾萬光年之外
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也一定會擊中他
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.95,0:08:38.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是雷電波濤
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.07,0:08:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.97,0:08:43.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你無法避開這鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:48.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,決勝負了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.74,0:08:55.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.37,0:08:57.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幹得好 
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.55,0:08:59.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,打倒一級刻鬥士啦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.27,0:09:03.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 剛才那招還蠻有趣的呢 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.43,0:09:05.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.82,0:09:06.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.96,0:09:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明直接擊中他了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.41,0:09:10.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種程度的攻擊 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.10,0:09:15.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是撫過我刻衣表面的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.30,0:09:21.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,睜大眼睛看好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.08,0:09:23.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是我的刻衣 
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.37,0:09:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重爆刻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.04,0:09:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的刻衣 重爆刻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.22,0:09:37.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天蠍座 山羊座 天秤座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.84,0:09:41.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,具備黃金聖衣的三個星座
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:44.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃金聖衣…三個？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.57,0:09:45.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有著三名黃金聖鬥士力量的一級刻鬥士
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.11,0:09:54.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎會是爾等青銅可對抗的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.78,0:10:05.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來已經黔驢技窮了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.75,0:10:06.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.47,0:10:14.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,戰鬥 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.71,0:10:15.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尚未結束呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:20.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星雲氣流
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.99,0:10:22.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那氣流之內 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.52,0:10:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是無法自由行動的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:26.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,停手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.04,0:10:29.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可不想傷害你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.24,0:10:32.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確是了不起的小宇宙呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.81,0:10:37.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.72,0:10:48.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,星雲氣流 居然…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.08,0:10:51.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這才叫做無法自由行動
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.72,0:10:54.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種重量是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.02,0:10:55.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是早就說過嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.25,0:10:58.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的劍可以支配重力
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.70,0:11:00.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,破壞大地
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.51,0:11:03.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力甚至可以吸引光
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.60,0:11:05.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.76,0:11:07.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重爆雷斬刃！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:33.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生！！！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.41,0:11:41.79,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈、聖劍的破壞力！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:48.32,remark,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,強烈、聖劍的破壞力！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.10,0:11:50.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.11,0:11:52.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.77,0:11:58.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類真是種天真的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.29,0:12:02.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仙女座一邊掩護著你們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.71,0:12:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一邊同我作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.88,0:12:04.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,掩護我們？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.18,0:12:09.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 他似乎沒能使出全力
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.54,0:12:10.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.14,0:12:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然為了我們
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.62,0:12:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這份天真成為了他的束縛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,最終害他丟掉了性命
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.64,0:12:21.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類的愚蠢 還真是有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.37,0:12:28.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒有結束
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.71,0:12:30.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦 還有意識嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.92,0:12:31.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.02,0:12:32.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.28,0:12:34.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.00,0:12:36.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃該翁 
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.44,0:12:38.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我應該說過
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.92,0:12:43.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,絕對不允許你…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.77,0:12:46.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,傷害他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.44,0:12:49.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體竟然…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.86,0:12:51.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,動彈不得
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.28,0:12:54.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒用的 根本動不了分毫
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.45,0:12:58.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛剛重爆雷斬刃的一擊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.00,0:13:03.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經將你身體的時間奪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.91,0:13:04.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.40,0:13:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是為了讓你親眼看著同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無比淒慘地死在自己的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.78,0:13:16.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這種絕望的狀況下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.46,0:13:19.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人類會做出怎樣的反應
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,且讓我觀察一番吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.81,0:13:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是太有趣了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.45,0:13:27.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 是一個一個來呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.14,0:13:31.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是一併解決了你們呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.78,0:13:38.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和傳言一樣 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:40.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還真是頑強啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.29,0:13:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說 為了我們戰鬥的瞬先生很天真吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.42,0:13:47.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那又如何 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:48.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我只是說了事實而已
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.01,0:13:49.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因為瞬先生的意志
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.47,0:13:55.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們才能夠重新站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.85,0:13:57.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生的溫柔 
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.80,0:14:00.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給了我們奮起再戰的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.42,0:14:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.61,0:14:03.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可不要小看人類啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.81,0:14:05.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該輪到我們
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.75,0:14:08.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保護瞬先生了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.80,0:14:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是個有趣的笑話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.63,0:14:16.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們要如何從我這重爆雷斬刃之下保護他
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.05,0:14:24.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.20,0:14:26.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重力可以扭曲時空
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,延緩時間的腳步
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.47,0:14:32.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因此 這把能夠支配重力的劍
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.62,0:14:35.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也可以自由地操控時間
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.53,0:14:42.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身…身體 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.99,0:14:44.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好重
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.96,0:14:49.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而以重力增加對手的負荷
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,封住對手的行動 亦是輕而易舉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.77,0:14:53.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.05,0:15:03.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,斬裂大地 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.93,0:15:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喚來雷光
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.36,0:15:10.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心 我已經手下留情了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.61,0:15:13.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼快就要了你們的命實在可惜
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.24,0:15:15.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還想多找點樂子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.05,0:15:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,先解除加在你們身上的重力吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:22.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 你們有何對策
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.85,0:15:26.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要如何打倒我埃該翁呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.38,0:15:29.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們根本無法靠近他
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.45,0:15:30.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們現在的狀況 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.15,0:15:32.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,完全束手無策啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.70,0:15:34.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到底該怎麼辦啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.25,0:15:36.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.80,0:15:38.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃該翁手中的聖劍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.06,0:15:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要沒有那把劍 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.82,0:15:42.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他就無法進行遠距離攻擊了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.30,0:15:45.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必須靠近那傢伙 
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.25,0:15:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,毀掉那把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.46,0:15:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂 你又想出這種魯莽的作戰
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.23,0:15:52.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 有道理
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.20,0:15:57.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所謂射人先射馬 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.80,0:15:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對戰蘇魯特的時候也是這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:02.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刻鬥士憑借武器增強力量
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.05,0:16:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反之 如果他們失去了武器…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.42,0:16:06.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要能摧毀那把劍
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.49,0:16:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.78,0:16:10.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣我們就會有勝算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.72,0:16:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.98,0:16:14.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞬先生的時間也一定會恢復
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.79,0:16:17.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來你們已經商量好了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.10,0:16:19.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來 你們又打算怎麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.44,0:16:22.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就這麼辦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.11,0:16:26.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬流星拳
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.18,0:16:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笑死人了 這種程度的攻擊 
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.42,0:16:36.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我們也上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:37.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.79,0:16:41.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,幼獅熾焰
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:45.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神聖龍捲風
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:48.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,成功了
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.03,0:16:51.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好極了 有效果
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:53.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白費力氣
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.22,0:16:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種小伎倆 根本沒用
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:58.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在我重爆雷斬刃的面前
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.84,0:17:00.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的這些彫蟲小技 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.43,0:17:02.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過是小孩子過家家而已
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.96,0:17:06.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼會…劍竟然分毫未損
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.54,0:17:08.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們耍完了嗎 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.36,0:17:10.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼該輪到我出招了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.21,0:17:18.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身體無法動彈了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.20,0:17:20.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有這點水平嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.15,0:17:20.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.89,0:17:23.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 真是辜負了我的期待
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.68,0:17:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,該給你們個痛快了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.21,0:17:28.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你可要看好了 仙女座的瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,住手！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.01,0:17:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接招吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.64,0:17:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蒼摩
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.39,0:17:56.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤娜 
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.08,0:17:57.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.73,0:18:02.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣 仙女座
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.74,0:18:04.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,失去同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.01,0:18:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你現在的心情如何
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.98,0:18:11.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不說我也知道
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.81,0:18:15.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那雙眼睛表明了一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.17,0:18:19.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當雅典娜的生命跡象消失的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.57,0:18:22.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你會做出何種反應
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.25,0:18:23.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說我也真想看看
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.97,0:18:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但情勢卻不容
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.00,0:18:30.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只好請你先雅典娜一步去了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.94,0:18:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.11,0:18:35.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.66,0:18:37.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,由天馬座發出的麼
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.89,0:18:39.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光…光牙？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:41.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然還有一口氣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.71,0:18:43.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,著實有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.61,0:18:45.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這力量到底是從什麼地方來的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.95,0:18:47.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,憑你是無法理解的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.86,0:18:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人是不會輕言放棄的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.16,0:18:52.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.49,0:18:54.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要有一絲希望的話
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.25,0:18:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不管多少次都會站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.44,0:18:58.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.00,0:19:02.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種情況你還要說有希望麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.56,0:19:03.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬座
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在此
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.12,0:19:09.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有這雙拳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.56,0:19:11.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,並且 我還有著
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.59,0:19:16.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能揮動這雙拳頭的小宇宙在
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.71,0:19:21.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算你還剩下些許小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.25,0:19:23.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也對我埃該翁無用
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.71,0:19:24.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不好說
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.93,0:19:25.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.98,0:19:28.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼近的距離 足夠我打到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.82,0:19:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這瀕死的拳頭
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看我用重爆雷斬刃來擋下來
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.01,0:19:37.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要在近距離下 打進這一拳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.56,0:19:40.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閃耀吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:42.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的小宇宙！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.41,0:19:48.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天馬彗星拳！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.81,0:19:55.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種玩意是不管用的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.40,0:19:57.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別小看人類！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.51,0:19:59.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.86,0:20:05.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,將小宇宙集中於了一點
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.19,0:20:22.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.14,0:20:23.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光牙
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:27.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說光牙將埃該翁打倒了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼 太天真了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.23,0:20:31.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種程度就以為能打倒我麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.58,0:20:32.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃該翁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.43,0:20:38.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好看看你的劍吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.36,0:20:39.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.85,0:20:40.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.27,0:20:42.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.42,0:20:44.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃該翁
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.76,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是人類的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.77,0:20:53.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,區區人類竟能在我的重爆雷斬刃上打出傷痕
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.32,0:20:54.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這點還是值得表揚一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.89,0:20:59.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是你好像連再揮動拳頭的小宇宙都沒有了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.76,0:21:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會讓你傷害光牙的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:06.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雖說你的時間恢復了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.75,0:21:09.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但也沒有能打倒我的力量吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.28,0:21:11.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有我們在
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:15.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對 我們四人一起上的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.22,0:21:17.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我還真是被小看了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.42,0:21:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算受到了損傷
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.08,0:21:21.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這重爆雷斬刃的力量也是絕大的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:24.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且這重爆刻衣
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.92,0:21:27.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們的小宇宙對它完全無效
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.63,0:21:28.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,作為陪我玩玩的感謝
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.99,0:21:30.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就將你們一起
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.09,0:21:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埋葬於這最高級的雷電之下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.82,0:21:42.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,的確非常有趣啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.45,0:21:46.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.14,0:21:50.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我可忘不了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.01,0:21:53.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種攻擊性的小宇宙
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.24,0:21:59.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.30,0:22:00.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰座 一輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:01.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.74,0:22:03.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,埃該翁
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.14,0:22:06.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為了與你做個了結
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.18,0:22:11.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鳳凰座一輝再次鳳舞歸來
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.75,0:22:14.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰座 一輝
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.78,0:22:15.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.06,0:22:18.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也厭倦了餘興節目了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.90,0:22:21.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看來能稍微讓我娛樂下了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.35,0:22:27.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鳳凰座的男子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.14,0:22:30.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在戰鬥之終末 迎來的是安詳麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.38,0:22:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男子答曰
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.05,0:22:33.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.14,0:22:35.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥爭才是本性
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.04,0:22:37.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煉獄即是故鄉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.21,0:22:40.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以紅蓮之火涼身
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.43,0:22:43.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不死鳥行於修羅之道
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.78,0:22:45.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下集 聖鬥士星矢Ω
Dialogue: 0,0:22:46.07,0:22:47.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鬥志的極致！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.68,0:22:49.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一輝對埃該翁！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.74,0:22:52.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你曾感受到小宇宙的存在嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,
